   218	      `(DataField, Array, int[] defLevels, int[] repLevels)` column triples, creates a ParquetWriter on a
   219	      provided Stream with `CompressionMethod = CompressionMethod.Zstd`, sets CustomMetadata, opens one
   220	      row group, and writes columns IN `schema.GetDataFields()` ORDER. Iterate `schema.GetDataFields()`
   221	      and pair each returned DataField with its matching caller-supplied array by DataField identity
