   336	- `dotnet test --filter MzPeakParquet` green (PQ-01, PQ-02 round-trip + def/rep lock + nullable PARAM).
   337	- End-to-end run on `small.RAW` exits 0 with no ERROR line and produces `<raw>.mzpeak`; structural gate
   338	  (STORED + index) passes; both parquet facets assert ZSTD column-chunk compression; reference Python
   339	  OPEN gate exits 0 (PQ-03).
   340	- `parseInput.Errors == 0 && parseInput.Warnings == 0` on the clean small.RAW.
   341	</verification>
