   248	
   249	## Unknown 4 — mzpeak_index.json minimum — DECISION: 2 file entries, empty metadata block
   250	
   251	[VERIFIED: schema/mzpeak_index.json requires only `files` + `metadata`; reader `_from_zip_archive`
